local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["floppy"]={"floppy","['flɒpɪ]","['flɑpi]","n.软盘",'adj.叭塌叭塌响的,懒散的,邋遢的|||n.软盘','In software protection, a method of giving a mark, or signature, that cannot be duplicated, to a floppy disk. A special test routine detects if a signature is present, and if it is not found the protected program will be disabled.','软件保护中，把不能复制的标记或签名存放在软盘上的方法，用一个特殊测试程序来检测签名是否存在，如不存在，则被保护的程序不能运行。','Can not save them to a network drive or a floppy disk.','不能救他们到一个网络驱动器或一个软盘。'}
